          "SAMPLE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "Natural isotopic composition zinc targets have been",
                "prepared by  evaporating metallic Zn onto  thin Al",
                "foil backings. The target thickness has been measured",
                "by  weighing and in some cases  checked by Rutherford",
                "Backscattering (RBS)."
              ]
            },
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": {
                "nuclide": "30-ZN-64",
                "field_identifier": "NAT",
                "value": 0.48268
              },
              "free_text": [
                ""
              ]
            },
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": {
                "nuclide": "30-ZN-66",
                "field_identifier": "NAT",
                "value": 0.27975
              },
              "free_text": [
                ""
              ]
            },
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": {
                "nuclide": "30-ZN-67",
                "field_identifier": "NAT",
                "value": 0.04102
              },
              "free_text": [
                ""
              ]
            },
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": {
                "nuclide": "30-ZN-68",
                "field_identifier": "NAT",
                "value": 0.19024
              },
              "free_text": [
                ""
              ]
            },
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": {
                "nuclide": "30-ZN-70",
                "field_identifier": "NAT",
                "value": 0.00631
              },
              "free_text": [
                ""
              ]
            }
          ],
          "DETECTOR": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "HPGE"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                ""
              ]
            }
          ],
          "METHOD": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "ACTIV",
                "SITA",
                "GSPEC"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                "The targets have been irradiated by",
                "the alpha-beam of the cyclotron accelerator of ATOMKI.",
                "The beam current was kept below 1 microA in order not",
                "to have target deterioration (the target stability was",
                "continuously monitored by RBS). The cross section",
                "was measured at nine different alpha-energies between",
                "6.3 and 9.5 MeV (lab.)irradiations lasted between 5",
                "and 18 hours depending on the energy. The decay of",
                "67Ga was followed for at least 12 hours."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "ADD-RES": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "THEO"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " The experimental data were compared to the",
                "results of the theoretical model codes TALYS, and",
                "NON-SMOKER."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "ERR-ANALYS": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": {
                "heading": "EN-ERR",
                "minimum_value": null,
                "maximum_value": null,
                "correlation_property": null
              },
              "free_text": [
                "The effective energies were calculated by",
                "taking into account the energy loss of the beam in the",
                "target. The uncertainty of the energy is the quadratic",
                "sum of the uncertainty of the beam energy (0.5%) and",
                "half of the energy loss in the target."
              ]
            },
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": {
                "heading": "DATA-ERR",
                "minimum_value": null,
                "maximum_value": null,
                "correlation_property": null
              },
              "free_text": [
                " The uncertainty of the cross section is the",
